Key Match Events: Isak scored two goals for Sweden in the 65th and 71st minutes.
Gyokeres scored a penalty for Sweden in the 80th minute.
Dadasov scored for Azerbaijan in the 82nd minute.
Wahlqvist received a yellow card in the 59th minute.
Saletros received a yellow card in the 90+1 minute.
Pre-Game Insights: Azerbaijan and Sweden will meet for a UEFA Nations League C clash in Baku on Thursday evening.
Sweden will be looking for a vast improvement on their most recent trip to Baku back in November 2023, when a three-goal defeat in Euro qualifying dealt their hopes of reaching Germany a major blow.
Sweden are heavy favourites to top a section containing Azerbaijan, Slovakia, and Estonia.
